<span class="line"><span style="color:#e1e4e8;">        Master locator : 官方 Set the queue into master location mode, determining the rule by which the queue master is located when declared on a cluster of nodes.(Sets the &quot;x-queue-master-locator&quot; argument.) </span></span>
